    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a true collector-grade vehicle in showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like shine with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple and matte, free of any bolster wear or creasing, and the original factory scent persists. Every electronic component and feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been maintained with an open-checkbook policy and a documented history of preventative maintenance. It has been strictly garage-kept under a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. For the buyer seeking a turn-key, investment-quality example that needs nothing, this is it.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
